OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFirms join forces to combat
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fracism in chemistry        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Leading firms have begun a scheme to   
OL,6, help black and minority ethnic students
OL,7, get jobs as chemistry researchers.     
OL,9,FThe initiative follows an investigation
OL,10,Fwhich found that racism was "pervasive"
OL,11,Fin chemistry research.                 
OL,13,FThere is just one black chemistry      
OL,14,Fprofessor in the UK and black people in
OL,15,Fthe field are less well paid and less  
OL,16,Flikely to get promotions.              
OL,18,FThe initiative, called Broadening      
OL,19,FHorizons, is led by the Royal Society  
OL,20,Fof Chemistry.                          
